 
                               L E X I
                        Java based Word Processor
                       

Requirements
------------

A Java 2 runtime (preferably JDK 1.2.2 from Sun). See
http://java.sun.com.

How to run
----------

Run with 

  java -jar bin/Lexi.jar

Under Windows, double-clicking Lexi.jar should do it.
You can create a shortcut for that file as well.

Contributing/Comments
---------------------

Please direct comments to the current maintainer,
Jose Solorzano, at jhsolorz@yahoo.com.

